sequenceDiagram
    actor Anggota
    participant View as Absensi Form
    participant Controller as AbsensiKegiatanController
    participant Model as AbsensiKegiatan
    participant Storage as File Storage

    Anggota->>View: Pilih Kegiatan untuk Absensi
    View->>Controller: GET /anggota/absensi-kegiatan/create
    Controller-->>View: Tampilkan Form

    Anggota->>View: Isi Form & Upload Bukti
    View->>Controller: POST /anggota/absensi-kegiatan
    
    Controller->>Storage: Store Image
    Storage-->>Controller: Return File Path
    
    Controller->>Model: Create Absensi Record
    Model-->>Controller: Success
    
    Controller-->>View: Redirect with Success
